Patrick Williams remembers a recurring promise between himself and former star running back Reggie Cole.
“It’s been tough," Williams said.
He was a running back and safety at Dallas Carter, and was a two-time All-District player.
He also player track & field and tennis at Dallas Carter.
The coach and the family reminisced on “the good old days.”“I know the family, and they trusted me with Reggie," Williams said.